spec_data.Name: perl-File-SearchPath
spec_data.Description:
This module provides the ability to search a path-like environment variable
for a file (that does not necessarily have to be an executable).
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:38:39 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Search for a file in an environment variable path
